Package: ncschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process North Carolina School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the North Carolina
    Department of Public Instruction (NC DPI). Provides functions for fetching
    enrollment data from the NC Statistical Profile system and transforming it
    into tidy format for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs,
    stats,
    utils
